{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"element.firstChild","mdn_url":"/ko/docs/Web/API/Node/firstChild","locale":"ko","native":"한국어","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/Node\"><code>Node</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Properties</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/baseURI\"><code>baseURI</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/Node/childNodes\"><code>childNodes</code></a></li><li><em><code>firstChild</code></em></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/isConnected\"><code>isConnected</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/Node/lastChild\"><code>lastChild</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/Node/nextSibling\"><code>nextSibling</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/nodeName\"><code>nodeName</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/nodeType\"><code>nodeType</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/nodeValue\"><code>nodeValue</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/Node/ownerDocument\"><code>ownerDocument</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/parentElement\"><code>parentElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/parentNode\"><code>parentNode</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/Node/previousSibling\"><code>previousSibling</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/Node/textContent\"><code>textContent</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Methods</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/Node/appendChild\"><code>appendChild()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/Node/cloneNode\"><code>cloneNode()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/compareDocumentPosition\"><code>compareDocumentPosition()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/Node/contains\"><code>contains()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/getRootNode\"><code>getRootNode()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/Node/hasChildNodes\"><code>hasChildNodes()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/Node/insertBefore\"><code>insertBefore()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/isDefaultNamespace\"><code>isDefaultNamespace()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/isEqualNode\"><code>isEqualNode()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/isSameNode\"><code>isSameNode()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/isSupported\"><code>isSupported()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/lookupNamespaceURI\"><code>lookupNamespaceURI()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/lookupPrefix\"><code>lookupPrefix()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/Node/normalize\"><code>normalize()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/removeChild\"><code>removeChild()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/Node/replaceChild\"><code>replaceChild()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Inheritance:</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":".ec.9a.94.ec.95.bd","title":"요약","isH3":true,"content":"<p>트리에서 노드의 첫 번째 자식이나 <code>null</code>(노드가 자식이 없으면)을 반환합니다.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":".ea.b5.ac.eb.ac.b8","title":"구문","isH3":true,"content":"<pre class=\"eval notranslate\"><em>childNode</em> =<em>node</em>.firstChild;\n</pre>\n\n<p><code>childNode</code>는 자식이 있으면 <code>node</code>의 첫 번째 자식 참조이고 없으면 <code>null</code>입니다.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":".ec.98.88","title":"예","isH3":true,"content":"<p>이 예는 <code>firstChild</code>의 쓰임과 공백 노드가 어떻게 이 프로퍼티 사용을 방해하는 지 실제로 보입니다. Gecko DOM에서 공백 처리에 관한 더 많은 정보는 <a href=\"#notes\">Notes</a> 절을 보세요.</p>\n\n<pre class=\"notranslate\">&lt;p id=\"para-01\"&gt;\n  &lt;span&gt;First span&lt;/span&gt;\n&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;script type=\"text/javascript\"&gt;\n  var p01 = document.getElementById('para-01');\n  alert(p01.firstChild.nodeName)\n&lt;/script&gt;\n</pre>\n\n<p>위에서, alert은 텍스트 노드가 여는 태그 &lt;p&gt;의 끝과 여는 태그 &lt;span&gt; 사이에 공백을 유지하여 삽입되었기 때문에 '#text'를 보입니다. space 하나에서 여럿, return, tab 등 <strong>어떤</strong> 공백이든 #text 노드에 삽입되게 됩니다.</p>\n\n<p>다른 #text 노드는 닫는 태그 &lt;/span&gt;과 닫는 태그 &lt;/p&gt; 사이에 삽입됩니다.</p>\n\n<p>이 공백을 소스에서 제거하면, #text 노드는 삽입되지 않고 span 요소가 paragraph의 첫 번째 자식이 됩니다.</p>\n\n<pre class=\"notranslate\">&lt;p id=\"para-01\"&gt;&lt;span&gt;First span&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n\n&lt;script type=\"text/javascript\"&gt;\n  var p01 = document.getElementById('para-01');\n  alert(p01.firstChild.nodeName)\n&lt;/script&gt;\n</pre>\n\n<p>이제 alert은 'SPAN'을 보입니다.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":".ec.a3.bc.ec.9d.98","title":"주의","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Gecko 기반 브라우저는 소스 마크업에서 공백을 나타내기 위해 문서 내에 텍스트 노드를 삽입합니다.\n    그러므로 예를 들어 <a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/Node/firstChild\" title=\"트리에서 노드의 첫 번째 자식이나 null(노드가 자식이 없으면)을 반환합니다.\" aria-current=\"page\"><code>Node.firstChild</code></a>나 <a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/Node/previousSibling\" title=\"Node.previousSibling은 읽기전용 속성이며 현재 호출하는 노드가 속해 있는 부모의 childNodes 목록에서 특정 자식 노드를 리턴하거나 childNodes 목록의 첫번째 노드일 경우 Null값을 리턴합니다.\"><code>Node.previousSibling</code></a>을 통해서 얻은 노드는 작성자가 얻으려 한 실제 요소와는\n    달리 공백 텍스트 노드를 참조할 지도 모릅니다. </p>\n\n    <p>더 많은 정보는 <a class=\"new only-in-en-us\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document_Object_Model/Whitespace\" rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Whitespace in the DOM (en-US)</a>과\n    <a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/DOM/faq.html#emptytext\" rel=\"noopener\">W3C DOM 3 FAQ: Why are some Text nodes empty?</a>를 보세요.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":".eb.aa.85.ec.84.b8","title":"명세","isH3":true,"content":"<p><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/REC-DOM-Level-1/level-one-core.html#attribute-firstChild\" rel=\" noopener\">DOM Level 1 Core: firstChild</a></p>\n\n<p><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/DOM-Level-2-Core/core.html#ID-169727388\" rel=\" noopener\">DOM Level 2 Core: firstChild</a></p>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"트리에서 노드의 첫 번째 자식이나 null(노드가 자식이 없으면)을 반환합니다.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Node.firstChild","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"Node.firstChild","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"element.firstChild","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Node.firstChild","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"element.firstChild","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"},{"title":"Node.firstChild","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"Node.firstChild","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"Node.firstChild","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"ko/web/api/node/firstchild","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ko/web/api/node/firstchild/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ko/docs/Web","title":"개발자를 위한 웹 기술"},{"uri":"/ko/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API"},{"uri":"/ko/docs/Web/API/Node","title":"Node"},{"uri":"/ko/docs/Web/API/Node/firstChild","title":"element.firstChild"}],"pageTitle":"element.firstChild - Web API | MDN","noIndexing":false}}